This paper focuses on analyzing the behavior of Android malware, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also uses advanced analysis techniques and machine learning algorithms, which are common in software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with large datasets and uses statistical analysis, which are relevant to data science (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG).
